            </h6>
            <p>I have learned that making mistakes is all part of the process of being a great successor. In order for us to learn better, we make mistakes. For the stack overflow, there were mistakes, but we learn from those mistakes when we debug them. Also, sometimes doing a process your own way is another method of learning.</p>
